messages.text: Hey...you still there?
Yes.
Ben’s heart sounded like the military drum corps in his chest.
Listen, I know it’s weird since we haven’t spoken in so long, but I’ve just had a shitty night.
I’m on my way.
But I didn’t tell you where I am.
Oh right...haha.
He then started to sweat.
You should probably know....and I’m embarrassed to admit...
I got a little covered in vomit.
So maybe bring a plastic bag or something for the seat
I’m sorry YOU WHAT?
Yeah...like I said: shitty night.
Simultaneously in another conversation -
YOU WANT TO TELL ME WHY SHE’S COVERED IN VOMIT?
Whoa, I just had a cop wrestle me to the fucking ground over the mask I told you I DIDN’T want to wear.
SO YOU CAN STEP THE FUCK BACK!!! Wait...
How did you know she’s covered in vomit
SHE TEXTED ME TO COME PICK HER UP!!
WHAT?!? She figured it out??
Her ride fell through. WHAT DO I DO!?
GO PICK HER UP DOUCHEBAG
YEAH BUT WHAT ELSE???
I don’t know man. Maybe play it by ear??
I don’t play things by ear!!
I planned a fucking flash mob in her honor tmrw because playing it by ear makes me turn into an idiot!
I kind of think the flash mob makes you an idiot, but that’s just me.
WHAT DO I DO
Okay, so one...
Maybe just act like a normal human being?
Maybe this is the universe’s way of making you act normal, instead of this mystery shit.
I feel like I’m going to throw up.
Maybe bring her a sweatshirt, and sweatpants, because you know...vomit.
I’m bookmarking my calendar for when I can kill you for that.
Maybe ask her to grab some food!?
GENIUS!!!!
One more thing. I need to borrow your car.
NO WAY DUDE. IM SUPPOSED TO MEET JESSE! YOU HAVE YOUR OWN!
MINE IS IN THE SHOP!!!
COME ON MAN AND MY PARENTS WON’T LET ME TAKE THEIRS!!
I'll go with you to meet Jesse, first. Then I'll take your car and bring it back later.
If I lend you my car, you better have it back before 11:30.
Because if I’m not home by 11:45, my parents will FREAK OUT.
Also one more thing. Bring me some of your Mom’s sweet ass banana cake.
Fine.
Ben is in the car with Alan, on the way to Jesse's.
Hey, I just got caught up in traffic for a little bit - be there soon!
Ok.
After staring at his phone trying to get the courage to ask her to eat, Alan takes his phone and does it for him.
Hey...by any chance are you hungry?
Would you want to grab a bite on the way home?
Ben screams at Alan, and pulls his hood over his head, hoping it will swallow him into some other dimension.
He hears a ding on his phone, and opens up his hood enough so one eye can see what was written.
I am hungry, but unfortunately don’t have any money on me.
Ben looks at Alan wide-eyed; he doesn’t have any money either.
Alan rolls his eyes, and gives him a $20.
I have money! My treat.
Really? You always were the nicest. And yes. Let’s stop for food.
30 minutes later, Ben is waiting outside the Magic Castle shaking in his car.
Dude, I’m freaking out.
Just breathe. And definitely don’t masturbate in my car.
WHAT!? WHY WOULD I DO THAT!
I do it sometimes to take the edge off before dates.
Ben immediately wipes the steering wheel with the sleeve of his sweatshirt.
While he’s doing it, the car door opens. It’s her, smiling wide.
2 hours later
DUDE! WHERE’S MY CAR!? AND NOT THE SHITTY ASHTON KUTCHER MOVIE!
Okay, so here’s the deal. I owe you my whole life right now.
While things were a bit awkward first...I ended up taking her to the diner.
We started talking about this park we used to ride our bikes to when we were kids.
Are you at the fucking park right now??
Yeah, but listen, she’s telling me about how she’s giving up on this “mystery guy” and I’m trying to get her to follow the next clue tomorrow.
Beyond the fact that I’m fucking hugely pissed off that you aren’t picking me up right now ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND!?
What??
You’re putting yourself in the friend-zone.
No, I’m just leading her straight to me.
No, you are setting her up to think there is some magical goddamn unicorn person meeting her, so her expectations are high.
So then what do I do??
Well, it’s too late now...just go along with it. Moron.
And I don’t know HOW ABOUT COME PICK ME UP YOU ASSHOLE!
20 minutes later
I told her that I think the clue is at Mt. Wilson, so she goes to the right place...
I offered to drive her : /
smh....
Just dropped her off.
She told me she wished she started hanging out with me more before I left town!!!
I OWE YOU MAN!!!
I’m going to go back to my original question of DUDE WHERE’S MY CAR!?
Okay, okay, okay...be there soon.
